## Quickstart

```bash
mise install && uv sync && just verify
```

## What this is

This project was scaffolded from [verify-kit](https://github.com/m2moiz/verify-kit) (`gh:m2moiz/verify-kit`) — a Copier-based template that bundles a self-verifiable agentic-coding harness. `just verify` is the single ground-truth command for both human developers and coding agents.

## Tooling

- **mise** — manages Python and Node toolchain versions via `.mise.toml`
- **just** — canonical task runner (`just --list` for all available commands)
- **pre-commit** — fast pre-commit hooks (ruff, biome, gitleaks, whitespace)
{% if has_backend %}
- **FastAPI + Postgres** — async backend with SQLAlchemy, Alembic, and Testcontainers
{% endif %}
{% if has_llm %}
- **LiteLLM + Langfuse** — LLM integration with cost tracking and observability
{% endif %}

